# GOLive Creator Studio Enhancements & Watch Page Fix

I have successfully resolved the 404 error on the watch page and transformed the upload process into a premium **Creator Studio** experience, incorporating advanced features from YouTube and Twitch.

## 🛠️ Critical Fix: Watch Page 404
The "Page Not Found" error was caused by a recent update in Next.js 16 where dynamic route `params` are now provided as a **Promise**. Accessing `params.id` directly was resulting in an `undefined` ID and triggering the `notFound()` block.

- **Fixed**: [app/watch/[id]/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Walt%20&%20Carter/.gemini/antigravity/playground/sonic-zenith/app/watch/%5Bid%5D/page.tsx) now properly awaits the `params` before querying Supabase.
- **Verification**: Local debug scripts confirmed the video data exists and is now accessible via the server query.

## 🚀 Creator Studio Enhancements

### 1. Advanced Upload Dashboard
The upload page now provides a professional, identity-focused experience with AI clipping and comment controls.

### 2. Studio Dashboard (`/studio/dashboard`)
Creators now have a powerful command center to manage their videos:
- **Dashboard UI**: Stats cards (Views, Subs, Revenue) and video management table.
- **Video Management**: Full support for deleting videos with instant UI updates.
- **Stats Recap**: Track total views, estimated revenue, and subscriber counts.
- **AI Studio Integration**: Direct links to the viral analysis tools.

### Discoverability & UI Refinements
- **YouTube-Scale Grid**: Increased thumbnail sizes and reduced column counts (max 4) to ensure high-impact visual presentation.
- **Community Hype Engine**: Added a "Hype" button that sends videos viral by boosting their algorithmic ranking.
- **Hype Badges**: Videos with high engagement now display a "Hyped" badge on their thumbnails.
- **Smart Filtering**: Category bar now includes a functional "Recent" filter for chronological browsing.
- **Ranking Algorithm**: Updated [vibe-rank.ts](file:///C:/GOLive/lib/vibe-rank.ts) to prioritize community hypes over standard likes.

### 3. Share Functionality
- Added a "Share" button to the watch page that instantly copies the video URL to the clipboard.

### 4. Critical Fixes
- **Integer 0.9 Mismatch**: Resolved a bug in the AI Studio clipping API that was sending raw float values to the database. All numeric outputs are now properly rounded.
- **Watch Page 404 Troubleshooting**: Added server-side diagnostic logs to track down remaining production-only fetch errors.

## 📦 Technical Details
- **Database**: 5 new columns added to the `videos` table (`allow_clipping`, `allow_comments`, `visibility`, `scheduled_for`, `license`).
- **Types**: Extended the global [Video](file:///C:/GOLive/types/index.ts#16-43) TypeScript interface for full type safety.
- **Build**: Successfully validated with `npm run build`.

